{
  "texts": [
    "Two thousand image patches and corresponding expression matrices were trained from 14 ST samples, and an extra 500 images patches were used for held-out validation.",
    "The learning rate was set as 0.001 with the Adam optimizer for training.",
    "Mean-squared loss was used to fit the predictions to the real ST images.",
    "The final paired synthetic histology images were generated by running the trained model.",
    "Signature gene set retrieval in simulated data."
  ]
}